OL,3,CDisability ministers will 'champion'
OL,4,Cinclusion and accessibility, says Timms
OL,6,FA designated disability minister will
OL,7,Fbe appointed to each Government
OL,8,Fdepartment to "champion disability
OL,9,Finclusion and accessibility", the
OL,10,FGovernment has announced.
OL,12,FWork and pensions minister Sir Stephen
OL,13,FTimms said the move aims to drive
OL,14,F"real improvements" for disabled
OL,15,Fpeople, whom the ministers will be
OL,16,Fencouraged to engage with on a regular
OL,17,Fbasis.
