OL,3,CDisability ministers will 'champion'
OL,4,Cinclusion and accessibility, says Timms
OL,6,FHe told the Commons: "I am very
OL,7,Fpleased to be able to announce today
OL,8,Fthe appointment of new lead ministers
OL,9,Ffor disability in each Government
OL,10,Fdepartment, they will represent the
OL,11,Finterests of disabled people, champion
OL,12,Fdisability inclusion and accessibility
OL,13,Fwithin their departments.
OL,15,F"I'm going to chair regular meetings
OL,16,Fwith them and will encourage them to
OL,17,Fengage directly with disabled people
OL,18,Fand their representative
OL,19,Forganisations, as they take forward
OL,20,Ftheir departmental priorities.
