OL,3,CDisability ministers will 'champion'
OL,4,Cinclusion and accessibility, says Timms
OL,6,F"And I look forward to this new group
OL,7,Fof lead ministers for disability
OL,8,Ftogether driving real improvements
OL,9,Facross Government for disabled people."
OL,11,FThis came during an adjournment debate
OL,12,Fon International Day of Persons with
OL,13,FDisabilities, where Liberal Democrat
OL,14,FMP Steve Darling raised concerns about
OL,15,F"floating bus stops", which have a
OL,16,Fcycle lane between the stop and the
OL,17,Fpavement.
