OL,3,CDisability ministers will 'champion'
OL,4,Cinclusion and accessibility, says Timms
OL,6,FIntervening, the MP for Torbay, who is
OL,7,Fregistered blind, said: "The
OL,8,FGovernment needs to ban floating bus
OL,9,Fstops."
OL,11,FSir Stephen said: "I do think this
OL,12,Fissue about floating bus stops is an
OL,13,Fimportant issue which we need to work
OL,14,Facross Government to reflect on."
OL,16,FLabour MP Debbie Abrahams, who led the
OL,17,Fdebate, had earlier criticised the
OL,18,Flack of accessibility for disabled
OL,19,Fpeople on trains.
