OL,6,FThe Oldham East and Saddleworth MP
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our train network does not have
OL,8,Flevel access, and we heard Dame Tanni
OL,9,FGrey-Thompson from the other place
OL,10,Fmake this plea back in the summer,
OL,11,Fabsolutely outrageous what she was put
OL,12,Fthrough.
OL,14,F"But I was absolutely shocked to find,
OL,15,Fwhen I had a presentation of the
OL,16,FTransPennine route upgrade, that the
OL,17,Frolling stock yet to be commissioned
OL,18,Fis not going to provide that level
OL,19,Faccess.
